---
// ServiceModals.astro - Pop-up modals for Technology & Systems service cards
---

<!-- MODAL: Video Analytics & Heatmapping -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-video-heatmap">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('video-heatmap')" aria-label="Stang">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi & System</span><span class="en-text">Technology & Systems</span></p>
      <h2>Video Analytics & Heatmapping</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Forvandla ditt befintliga CCTV-system till ett kraftfullt analysverktyg. Var losning ar kompatibel med alla kameraplattformar vi testat - ingen ny hardvara kravs.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">Turn your existing CCTV system into a powerful analytics tool. Compatible with all camera platforms we have tested - no new hardware required.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/heatmap-store.jpg" alt="Store heatmap" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Heatmap overview</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/cctv-retail.jpg" alt="CCTV retail" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>AXIS camera in store</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Kompatibelt med alla CCTV-system</strong><strong class="en-text">Compatible with all CCTV systems</strong><span class="sv-text">Koppla pa var analysmodul mot din befintliga infrastruktur - AXIS, Hanwha, Hikvision m.fl.</span><span class="en-text">Connect our analytics module to your existing infrastructure - AXIS, Hanwha, Hikvision and more.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Varma och kalla zoner</strong><strong class="en-text">Hot and cold zones</strong><span class="sv-text">Se tydligt vilka delar av butiken som attraherar flest kunder och vilka ytor som underprestererar.</span><span class="en-text">See clearly which parts of the store attract the most customers and which areas underperform.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Realtidsanalys och trender</strong><strong class="en-text">Real-time analysis and trends</strong><span class="sv-text">Folj kundfloden live eller analysera rorselsemonster over tid - per veckodag, kampanjperiod eller sasong.</span><span class="en-text">Monitor customer flows live or analyze movement patterns over time - by weekday, campaign period or season.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Floden och genvagar</strong><strong class="en-text">Flows and shortcuts</strong><span class="sv-text">Identifiera vilka rutter kunderna tar, var de stannar upp och var de passerar utan att engagera sig.</span><span class="en-text">Identify which routes customers take, where they stop and where they pass without engaging.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Intryck och besokstid</strong><strong class="en-text">Impressions and dwell time</strong><span class="sv-text">Mat genomsnittlig besokstid per zon och se vilka exponeringsytor som skapar verklig uppmarksamhet.</span><span class="en-text">Measure average dwell time per zone and see which display areas generate real attention.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Mobil dashboard</strong><strong class="en-text">Mobile dashboard</strong><span class="sv-text">Atkomst till heatmaps och nyckeltal direkt i mobilen - for butikschefen i farten.</span><span class="en-text">Access heatmaps and KPIs directly on mobile - for the store manager on the go.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>4-15%</strong><span class="sv-text">forsaljningsvaxkt</span><span class="en-text">sales growth</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>80+</strong><span class="sv-text">genomforda projekt</span><span class="en-text">completed projects</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Alla CCTV</strong><strong class="en-text">All CCTV</strong><span class="sv-text">kompatibelt</span><span class="en-text">compatible</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MODAL: Video Shelf Analytics -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-video-shelf-analytics">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('video-shelf-analytics')" aria-label="Stang">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi & System</span><span class="en-text">Technology & Systems</span></p>
      <h2>Video Shelf Analytics</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Forsta exakt vilka hyllor, gavlar och stortar som ar butikens mest attraktiva placeringar. Var AI-modell tolkar din butiksritning och mappar ut alla zoner automatiskt.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">Understand exactly which shelves, end caps and dump bins are your store's most attractive placements. Our AI model interprets your store sketch and maps all zones automatically.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall"><img src="/images/services/storesketch.jpg" alt="Store sketch zone mapping" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Store sketch - AI zone mapping</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap tall"><img src="/images/services/shelf-heatmap.jpg" alt="Shelf heatmap" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Shelf heatmap</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Automatisk zonmappning</strong><strong class="en-text">Automatic zone mapping</strong><span class="sv-text">Ladda upp din butiksritning. Var AI identifierar automatiskt alla hyllsektioner, gavlar och stortar.</span><span class="en-text">Upload your store sketch. Our AI automatically identifies all shelf sections, end caps and dump bins.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Varma och kalla hyllzoner</strong><strong class="en-text">Hot and cold shelf zones</strong><span class="sv-text">Se exakt var kunderna stannar upp och engagerar sig - och vilka hyllsektioner som passeras utan uppmarksamhet.</span><span class="en-text">See exactly where customers stop and engage - and which shelf sections are passed without attention.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Optimal produktplacering</strong><strong class="en-text">Optimal product placement</strong><span class="sv-text">Kombinera hyllanalys med forsaljningsdata (POS) for att identifiera vilka produkter som bor exponeras var.</span><span class="en-text">Combine shelf analytics with sales data (POS) to identify which products should be placed where.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Gavlar och stortar</strong><strong class="en-text">End caps and dump bins</strong><span class="sv-text">Identifiera dina mest premium-exponeringsytor med faktiska besoksdata som beslutsunderlag.</span><span class="en-text">Identify your most premium display spaces with real visitor data as the basis for decisions.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Kompatibelt med befintlig CCTV</strong><strong class="en-text">Compatible with existing CCTV</strong><span class="sv-text">Inget behov av ny hardvara - systemet integreras mot din befintliga kamerainfrastruktur.</span><span class="en-text">No need for new hardware - the system integrates with your existing camera infrastructure.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Trendanalys</strong><strong class="en-text">Trend analysis</strong><span class="sv-text">Jamfor hyllzonernas prestation under kampanjperioder mot normaltrafik och optimera lopande.</span><span class="en-text">Compare shelf zone performance during campaign periods against normal traffic and optimize continuously.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>4-15%</strong><span class="sv-text">forsaljningsvaxkt</span><span class="en-text">sales growth</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>AI-driven</strong><span class="sv-text">zonmappning</span><span class="en-text">zone mapping</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Alla CCTV</strong><strong class="en-text">All CCTV</strong><span class="sv-text">kompatibelt</span><span class="en-text">compatible</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MODAL: RFID & Scanning -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-rfid">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('rfid')" aria-label="Stang">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi & System</span><span class="en-text">Technology & Systems</span></p>
      <h2>RFID &amp; Scanning</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Genom att implementera RFID langs hela vardekedjan kan du eliminera administrativa fel, reducera svinn med upp till 40% och fa realtidskontroll pa varje enskild artikel.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">By implementing RFID along the entire value chain you can eliminate administrative errors, reduce waste by up to 40% and gain real-time control of every single item.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images trio">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/rfid-tags.jpg" alt="RFID tags" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>RFID tags</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/rfid-handheld.jpg" alt="Handheld scanner" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Handheld scanner</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/rfid-warehouse.jpg" alt="Warehouse scanner" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Warehouse scanner</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">RFID-taggar pa alla produkter</strong><strong class="en-text">RFID tags on all products</strong><span class="sv-text">Tagga varor i hela vardekedjan. Las av upp till 8 meters rackvidd utan siktlinje.</span><span class="en-text">Tag products throughout the value chain. Read up to 8 metres range without line of sight.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Handhallna skanners</strong><strong class="en-text">Handheld scanners</strong><span class="sv-text">Anvands for varumottagning, inventeringar och stickprov i butik. Snabbt, korrekt och mobilt.</span><span class="en-text">Used for goods receiving, stocktaking and spot checks in store. Fast, accurate and mobile.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Butiksportar och grindar</strong><strong class="en-text">Shop gates and portals</strong><span class="sv-text">Kontrollera svinnet vid utgangen - dubbelrollen som stoldskydd och logistikverktyg ger omedelbar ROI.</span><span class="en-text">Control shrinkage at the exit - the dual role as theft prevention and logistics tool delivers immediate ROI.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Lagertunnlar</strong><strong class="en-text">Warehouse tunnels</strong><span class="sv-text">Scanna en hel lastpall pa sekunder. Dramatisk tidsvinst vid in- och utleverans.</span><span class="en-text">Scan an entire pallet in seconds. Dramatic time savings during inbound and outbound deliveries.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Systemintegration</strong><strong class="en-text">System integration</strong><span class="sv-text">RFID-data kopplas mot ERP, POS och WMS for fullstandig sparbarhet och automatiska pafyllnadsregler.</span><span class="en-text">RFID data connects to ERP, POS and WMS for full traceability and automatic replenishment rules.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Skalbart och framtidsakert</strong><strong class="en-text">Scalable and future-proof</strong><span class="sv-text">Starta med ett lager eller en butik - skala upp i din takt. Tekniken ar beprovat och mogen.</span><span class="en-text">Start with one warehouse or one store - scale up at your own pace. The technology is proven and mature.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">upp till 40%</strong><strong class="en-text">up to 40%</strong><span class="sv-text">minskat admin-svinn</span><span class="en-text">reduced admin waste</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>8 m</strong><span class="sv-text">lasrackvidd</span><span class="en-text">read range</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Snabb ROI</strong><strong class="en-text">Fast ROI</strong><span class="sv-text">beprovad teknik</span><span class="en-text">proven technology</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MODAL: Digital Pricing -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-digital-prissattning">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('digital-prissattning')" aria-label="Stang">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi & System</span><span class="en-text">Technology & Systems</span></p>
      <h2><span class="sv-text">Digital prissattning</span><span class="en-text">Digital Pricing</span></h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Prisutvecklingen gar allt snabbare och gransen mellan fysisk och digital handel suddas ut. Elektroniska hyllkantsetiketter och smart prismjukvara ger dig full kontroll i realtid.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">The pace of price changes is accelerating and the boundary between physical and digital commerce is blurring. Electronic shelf labels and smart pricing software give you full control in real time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/esl-shelf.jpg" alt="Electronic shelf labels" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Electronic shelf labels</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/pricing-dashboard.jpg" alt="Pricing dashboard" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Pricing dashboard</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Elektroniska hyllkantsetiketter (ESL)</strong><strong class="en-text">Electronic Shelf Labels (ESL)</strong><span class="sv-text">Uppdatera tusentals priser med ett knapptryck. Eliminera felprismарkning och manuellt arbete.</span><span class="en-text">Update thousands of prices at the touch of a button. Eliminate pricing errors and manual work.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Fyra etikettsformat</strong><strong class="en-text">Four label formats</strong><span class="sv-text">Hook clip, Shelf clip, Product present och XL - ratt format for varje exponeringstyp och produktvarde.</span><span class="en-text">Hook clip, Shelf clip, Product present and XL - the right format for every display type and product value.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Konkurrentovervakning</strong><strong class="en-text">Competitor monitoring</strong><span class="sv-text">Bevaka omvarldens priser automatiskt och reagera proaktivt utan manuell research.</span><span class="en-text">Automatically monitor competitor pricing and react proactively without manual research.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Regelbaserad prissattning</strong><strong class="en-text">Rule-based pricing</strong><span class="sv-text">Bygg upp smarta prisregler som hanterar marginal, volym och kategori - helt automatiskt.</span><span class="en-text">Build smart pricing rules that handle margin, volume and category - fully automatically.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Stegvis implementering</strong><strong class="en-text">Phased implementation</strong><span class="sv-text">Starta manuellt for att lara dig mekanismerna. Lagg till semi- och helautomatik i din takt.</span><span class="en-text">Start manually to learn the mechanics. Add semi- and full automation at your own pace.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Bred teknologiintegration</strong><strong class="en-text">Broad technology integration</strong><span class="sv-text">Vi har erfarenhet av de flesta plattformar och hjalper dig valja ratt partner for din bransch.</span><span class="en-text">We have experience of most platforms and help you choose the right partner for your industry.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Realtid</strong><strong class="en-text">Real-time</strong><span class="sv-text">prisuppdateringar</span><span class="en-text">price updates</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Noll fel</strong><strong class="en-text">Zero errors</strong><span class="sv-text">prисmarkering</span><span class="en-text">in pricing</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Skalbar</strong><strong class="en-text">Scalable</strong><span class="sv-text">implementering</span><span class="en-text">implementation</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MODAL: Kiosk & Self-Service -->
