        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Surfplatta-POS</strong><strong class="en-text">Tablet POS</strong><span class="sv-text">iPad eller Android-surfplatta med standardkomponenter - snabb implementering, lag investering.</span><span class="en-text">iPad or Android tablet with standard components - fast implementation, low investment.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">All-in-one losningar</strong><strong class="en-text">All-in-one solutions</strong><span class="sv-text">Industristandardkabinett for butiker som vill ha en robust, skalbar och valbeprovat plattform.</span><span class="en-text">Industry-standard cabinet for stores wanting a robust, scalable and well-proven platform.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Informationskiosker med POS</strong><strong class="en-text">Information kiosks with POS</strong><span class="sv-text">Kombinera produktinfo, sjalvscanning och betalning i en enda kontaktpunkt mitt i butiken.</span><span class="en-text">Combine product information, self-scanning and payment in a single touchpoint in the store.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Kundresan i fokus</strong><strong class="en-text">Customer journey focus</strong><span class="sv-text">Vi designar losningar som ar intuitiva och enkla att adoptera - for alla kundgrupper.</span><span class="en-text">We design solutions that are intuitive and easy to adopt - for all customer groups.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong class="sv-text">Win-win for butik och kund</strong><strong class="en-text">Win-win for store and customer</strong><span class="sv-text">Lagre personalkostnader vid toppar, kortare kon och en upplevelse kunderna faktiskt uppskattar.</span><span class="en-text">Lower staff costs at peak times, shorter queues and an experience customers actually appreciate.</span></p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="effect-row">
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Kortare kon</strong><strong class="en-text">Shorter queues</strong><span class="sv-text">nojdare kunder</span><span class="en-text">happier customers</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong class="sv-text">Lagre kostnad</strong><strong class="en-text">Lower cost</strong><span class="sv-text">per transaktion</span><span class="en-text">per transaction</span></div>
        <div class="effect-badge"><strong>4</strong><span class="sv-text">format att valja</span><span class="en-text">formats available</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-cta"><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal sv-text">Kontakta oss</a><a href="/Contact/" class="btn-modal en-text">Contact us</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MODAL: NPS & Customer Analytics -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modal-nps-analytics">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeModal('nps-analytics')" aria-label="Stang">&#x2715;</button>
      <p class="modal-tag"><span class="sv-text">Teknologi & System</span><span class="en-text">Technology & Systems</span></p>
      <h2>NPS &amp; Customer Analytics</h2>
      <p class="lead sv-text">Vi har arbetat med kundnojdhetsmätningar i over 20 ar och ar fortfarande forvаnade over foretag som inte systematiskt samlar in och agerar pa kundfeedback.</p>
      <p class="lead en-text">We have worked with customer satisfaction measurement for over 20 years and are still surprised by companies that do not systematically collect and act on customer feedback.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="modal-images">
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/nps-feedback-app.jpg" alt="Feedback App" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>Feedback App</span></div>'" /></div>
        <div class="modal-img-wrap"><img src="/images/services/nps-dashboard.jpg" alt="NPS Dashboard" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='<div class=img-placeholder><span>NPS Dashboard</span></div>'" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-features">
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong>Net Promoter Score (NPS)</strong><span class="sv-text">Branschens basta metod for att mata kundlojalitet och jamfora resultat over tid, butik och kategori.</span><span class="en-text">The industry's best method for measuring customer loyalty and comparing results over time, store and category.</span></p></div>
        <div class="feature-item"><div class="feature-dot"></div><p><strong>Feedback | App</strong><span class="sv-text">Var egenutvecklade feedbackapp samlar in kundrespons i realtid - i kassan, via QR-kod eller mobil.</span><span class="en-text">Our own feedback app collects customer responses in real time - at checkout, via QR code or mobile.</span></p></div>
